Classifier: ChimeraX :: Bundle :: General :: 1,1 :: chimerax.tut_cmd ::  :: 
Classifier: ChimeraX :: Command :: tutorial cofm :: General ::

      Print center of mass of atoms
Classifier: ChimeraX :: Command :: tutorial highlight :: General ::

      Highlight atoms near center of mass
Requires-Python: >=3.7

Example code for implementing ChimeraX bundle.


Implements commands "tutorial cofm" to print the center of mass of a

set of atoms, and "tutorial highlight" to highlight the atoms nearest

the center of mass.
